# Code owners for dotnet-move.
#
# The repository owner is the sole code owner: every path requires their review. This is enforced on
# `develop` through branch protection (require_code_owner_reviews), so contributor branches off
# develop merge only after an owner approval. The owner retains an admin bypass (enforce_admins is
# off on develop) for their own work and the release prepare step, which they cannot self-approve.

